{"tid":2033690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮上個月話收到情報中共想將香港「全面西藏化」，初頭自己都半信半疑，而家睇黎係堅料","createTime":"2020-05-24T21:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T22:16:52.000Z","uid":60665,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0e8bf7a9029463806a2e3928730c8d897cd72b","tid":2033690,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:01:27.000Z","msg":"白宮上個月話收到情報中共想西藏化香港，初頭都50/50，而家睇黎係80/20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年推倒左條送中仲以為可以捱多幾年，估唔到一年後中共就大反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過中共港共一年對反對勢力既暴力鎮壓之後，今次個勢仲好似無晒還擊之力，估唔到最後都係要走到移民最後一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個月:<br />\n美國學者：有情報顯示中共已研判將香港「全面西藏化」 （Full Tibet)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1980038/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1980038/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3a82623f204cd6c2bdc57fe64a12fc28b29a802f","tid":2033690,"uid":60665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:03:48.000Z","msg":"香港100年既奇蹟睇黎好快進入終章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146c394db875f53cae5cb1d27b59d1331f4b0ecf","tid":2033690,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyT